# Keep audio-pipeline source artifacts out of the Vercel deploy upload.
# These are NOT served by the app (getAudioManifest only reads
# public/audio/{en,zh}/<slug>/), they only exist locally for the TTS +
# speed-variant pipeline. Shipping them was bloating "Deploying outputs"
# (~113 MB of 182 MB) and timing out production deploys.
#
# NOTE: only excludes non-served files. The live en/zh narration and the
# en fast/ variants still ship via Vercel. manifest.json is NOT excluded —
# audio.ts reads it from the filesystem at build time.

# Raw ElevenLabs originals (source for scripts/make-audio-variant.ts)
public/audio/*/*/candidates/

# ElevenLabs TTS mirror outputs (intermediate; app reads en/ and zh/, not *_tts/)
public/audio/en_tts/
public/audio/zh_tts/
